data.description: This one of a kind log home in the hills is close to town, while still enjoying two private acres on a hard surface road that back onto an expansive timber with tons of wildlife. The finishes throughout exude a lodge-like feel as though you are secluded in the mountains. The enormous great room will take your breath away and features tall cathedral ceilings and a massive stone fireplace. The open kitchen offers granite counters, custom cabinetry and high end appliances that all remain. This home offers 5 generously sized bedrooms, 3 full baths, main floor laundry and a fully finished walk-out lower level with complete mother-in-law suite with 2nd kitchen. The property offers tons of space to entertain, stunning hill-top views, and a large detached shop for your hobbies!
